sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as PIIApp
    participant Store as AppState
    participant HW as HardwareDetector
    participant AI as AIEngine
    participant PDF as PDFEngine
    participant Map as PIIMapper
    participant Canvas as RedactionCanvas
    participant Surg as Surgeon

    Note over User,Surg: Phase 1 — Upload and Scan

    User->>UI: Upload PDF file
    UI->>Store: setStatus("loading-model")
    UI->>HW: getHardwareTier()
    HW-->>UI: tier HIGH or LOW
    UI->>Store: setHardwareTier(tier)

    UI->>AI: loadModel(tier, onProgress)
    AI->>AI: Dynamic import transformers
    AI->>AI: pipeline token-classification
    AI-->>UI: inferenceFn

    UI->>Store: setStatus("processing")
    UI->>PDF: processPDF(file)
    PDF->>PDF: Parse PDF via pdfjs-dist
    PDF->>PDF: Render pages to canvas 3x scale
    PDF->>PDF: Extract TextTokens with coordinates
    PDF-->>UI: pageData and originalBytes

    loop For each page
        UI->>AI: inferenceFn(page.fullText)
        AI->>AI: NER inference plus regex patterns
        AI-->>UI: piiEntities[]
        UI->>Map: mapPIIToCoordinates(tokens, entities)
        Map->>Map: Fuzzy match tokens to entities
        Map->>Map: Apply CATEGORY_MAP labels
        Map->>Map: Set isActive = true
        Map-->>UI: RedactionBox[]
    end

    UI->>Store: setDraftBoxes(allBoxes)
    UI->>Store: setStatus("reviewing")

    Note over User,Surg: Phase 2 — Review and Toggle

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        User->>Canvas: Click a redaction box
        Canvas->>Store: toggleBox(id)
        Store->>Store: Flip isActive for box

        User->>UI: Check or uncheck category checkbox
        UI->>Store: toggleCategory(category, isActive)
        Store->>Store: Set isActive for all boxes in category
    end

    User->>Canvas: Enable Draw Mode
    Canvas->>Store: toggleDrawMode()
    User->>Canvas: Draw rectangle on page
    Canvas->>Store: addBox with x y w h page
    Store->>Store: Assign UUID and isActive = true

    Note over User,Surg: Phase 3 — Finalize and Download

    User->>UI: Click Finalize Redactions
    UI->>Store: setStatus("processing")
    UI->>UI: Filter draftBoxes where isActive is true
    UI->>Surg: applyRedactions(pageData, activeBoxes)

    loop For each page
        Surg->>Surg: Load preview image onto Canvas
        Surg->>Surg: Burn black rectangles into pixels
        Surg->>Surg: Export as flat JPEG
        Surg->>Surg: Add to jsPDF document
    end

    Surg-->>UI: Uint8Array redacted PDF
    UI->>UI: Create Blob URL
    UI->>Store: setRedactedPdfUrl(url)
    UI->>Store: setStatus("completed")

    Note over User,Surg: Phase 4 — Download and Wipe

    User->>UI: Preview redacted PDF in iframe
    User->>UI: Click Download PDF
    UI->>User: Browser downloads redacted_document.pdf
    UI->>UI: setTimeout 500ms
    UI->>Store: reset()
    Store->>Store: Revoke Blob URL
    Store->>Store: Clear all state
